title: Amanda Seals Interview and More
itunes:title: Amanda Seals Interview and More
description:
Wednesday 8/9 - Today we had good friend to the show Amanda Seales stop by, and dishes on the drama between her and Marsha Ambrosius, getting fired because of Jay-Z, and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Jessie Watters because of the comments he made about Colin Kaepernick and Angela Yee helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
